crowdsourced_ai_results.analysis: The script changes the current working directory to `/tmp`. It then downloads a remote file from `http://184.174.32.240:9000/bpexch_implant_linux` and saves it locally as `i`. Following the download, it grants execute permissions to the file `i` and executes it in the background, detaching it from the terminal and redirecting all its output to `/dev/null`.
